+ *   - Too short (≤200ms): synth fires while receiver is still doing
+ *     legit work; sender continues with potentially-wrong reply value
+ *     and TH-U state machine gets confused → crash at +0x1802DF0C3.
+ *   - Too long (≥1000ms): popup-click compounds many cycles into a
+ *     multi-second UI hang and Android marks the app ANR-frozen.
+ *   500ms hits the sweet spot in testing — short enough to keep total
